[SN]TITLE[SN]
Get Inspired: Ben Smith's 401 marathons challenge nears finish

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
In the last year, Ben Smith has run over 10,000 miles across Britain in all weather and is nearing the end of his challenge to run 401 marathons on consecutive days.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
